  "detailed_description": "<strong>Estimated Runtime: 60 - 90 mins </strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948790/extras/b898ffdea7be543a9d83c1a97a0b7731.poster.avif?t=1761150659\" width=616 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948790/extras/b898ffdea7be543a9d83c1a97a0b7731.webm?t=1761150659\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948790/extras/b898ffdea7be543a9d83c1a97a0b7731.mp4?t=1761150659\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948790/extras/d99fdf3f6fdf9f844d737faa44c77c65.avif?t=1761150659\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948790/extras/0edc94e4c61a154b5c0ad26bf2c8340c.poster.avif?t=1761150659\" width=616 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948790/extras/0edc94e4c61a154b5c0ad26bf2c8340c.webm?t=1761150659\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948790/extras/0edc94e4c61a154b5c0ad26bf2c8340c.mp4?t=1761150659\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>It begins when an unknown victim gives you the briefcase. Now it is yours, keep it safe, away from the entity.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948790/extras/7f9d340f832668a50643ff824dd2c5a9.avif?t=1761150659\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948790/extras/0cb7caee26c1f0cb7bfd9edf2565a29f.poster.avif?t=1761150659\" width=616 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948790/extras/0cb7caee26c1f0cb7bfd9edf2565a29f.webm?t=1761150659\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948790/extras/0cb7caee26c1f0cb7bfd9edf2565a29f.mp4?t=1761150659\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>It emerges from the shadows and it blends with the crowd. It won’t stop and you must plan and strategize to keep your distance.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948790/extras/ffe6263be9c132575803fb311396cd04.avif?t=1761150659\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948790/extras/0d235221166c3426edd049297172d77d.poster.avif?t=1761150659\" width=616 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948790/extras/0d235221166c3426edd049297172d77d.webm?t=1761150659\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948790/extras/0d235221166c3426edd049297172d77d.mp4?t=1761150659\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Your overworked lungs are on borrowed time. A humble inhaler is the lifeline that will give you the boost you need. Requires a few shakes to prime.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948790/extras/84bb17dc954ce4e41be1aff18a21cd0c.avif?t=1761150659\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948790/extras/1df285691298e2b327c10c5ad596fe14.poster.avif?t=1761150659\" width=616 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948790/extras/1df285691298e2b327c10c5ad596fe14.webm?t=1761150659\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2948790/extras/1df285691298e2b327c10c5ad596fe14.mp4?t=1761150659\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Your only option is to push through the sea of bodies, the amalgam of faces, the claustrophobia of the crowd. It could be any of them.<br><br><strong>Whether it's in a subway, nightclub, or riot-filled streets, do what you must to survive.</strong>",
